curation_metadata.curated_by: Claude Code - Phase 5 v3 GATE-compliant basket generation
notes: Strict GATE compliance - all Spanish words from taught LEGOs only
Distribution per basket: 2 short (1-2), 2 quite short (3), 2 longer (4-5), 4 long (6+)
First 2 phrases can be fragments, remaining 8 must be complete thoughts
Final phrase of final LEGO includes complete seed sentence
Prioritized recency: vocab from 5 previous seeds
English gerund grammar: 'enjoy speaking' not 'enjoy to speak'
